          "plain_text": "Running down with Kim and I’m watching the cyclists come past again - helicopters overhead. The waves are objectively better than yesterday morning - wrapping from behind the rocks all the way through the sandbar. There are no waves that are too big, and the smaller ones have a great line to them. ",
