    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The views and paths were breathtaking. I encounter two dogs and they come running from far away to confront me. I am carrying a stick this time and they don’t come too close. I run off from them down to the beach and plod along the sand. I can feel by confidence building around the dogs and they obviously can sense that. ",
            "link": null
          },
